data.description: Assumable loan at a 4.5% interest rate! This beautifully laid out one owner home, built in 2015, has 9 ft ceilings and smooth walls making the rooms feel bigger, brighter and more elegant than most newer homes today. You will find no wasted space in the 1,735 sq ft with 4 good sized bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms. Cook like a pro in a spacious kitchen with granite counters, and with the upgraded cabinets you will enjoy organizing all your kitchen needs. The Breakfast Bar gives you more space for food preparation, dining, or even doing homework! The big master suite with new carpets and a beautiful en suite bathroom provide plenty of space for two individuals to get ready with less stress. And with a walk-in shower the bathroom is gives more convenience and accessibility. The built-in fire pit creates a cozy atmosphere outdoors whether you're hosting an outdoor party after the summer sun has gone down, or you want to snuggle up with your family and chat into the early hours. You will be able to keep all of your laundry supplies in one place, including detergent bottles, fabric softener, and a laundry basket in the interior laundry room for the ultimate organization. All in all, you will not want to miss out on making this beautiful home yours! Don't hesitate to schedule your showing today!
